column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  s.class, s.z as redshift,  petroR5#_r, st.logmass FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyNoDust AS st ON st.specObjID = p.objid WHERE   p.u BETWEEN # AND #  AND g BETWEEN # AND #  AND s.class = GALAXY
